desc.en: Use the given message as the commit message. In addition, the -a flag will commit files that have been modified since the last commit. If multiple -m options are given, their values are concatenated as separate paragraphs. The -a combines git add and git commit.
Tell the command to automatically stage files that have been modified and deleted, but new files you have not told Git about are not affected
